These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: grey, brown, lavender, pink, aquamarine, white, turquise
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, tulip, orchid, sunflower, azalea, zinnia
 1. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes turquise##2
 2. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who growstulip and the person who growssunflower##2
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growstulip##2
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes white##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
11. the person who likes white is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Color   | pink | grey | turquise | brown    | lavender | aquamarine   | white    |
| Flower         | azalea  | bellflower   | orchid | poppy | tulip   | zinnia | sunflower |

