.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, musical, time-travel, disaster, action, documentary, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, pop, disco, house, folk, salsa, metal
1. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the fan salsa##2
3. the fan pop is on the right of the fan trance##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the fan disco##1
5. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
6. the fan folk is on the left of the fan trance##1
7. the fan metal is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the left of the fan house##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre          | action | time-travel | documentary | musical | crime | drama      | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | house  | metal     | disco     | folk  | trance | pop |

