.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
City: hamburg, marseilles, miami, liverpool, colone, boston, edinburgh
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, golf, sailing, rowing, cycling, soccer, weightlifting
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| City   | edinburgh | colone | hamburg | marseilles   | liverpool | miami | boston |
| Sport           | cycling | soccer     | golf     | sailing | rowing   | water-polo   | weightlifting    |

