.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  paramedic, manager, chef, scientist, social-worker, journalist, electrician
7 different games are played: snooker, billiard, whist, mah-jongg, scrabble, monopoly, poker
 1. the electrician is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the social-worker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the social-worker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the paramedic##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is between the chef and the person playing monopoly##2
 7. the paramedic is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the scientist##1
 9. the manager is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person playing snooker is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Job      | chef    | social-worker  | scientist  | paramedic  | electrician      | journalist       | manager |
| Game   | scrabble | mah-jongg | monopoly | poker | snooker | whist | billiard  |

