3. the person traveling to miami is between the brazilian and the dutch##2
4. the turkish is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person traveling to miami is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the dutch##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person traveling to boston is the polish##1
9. the thai is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Nationality   | polish      | thai | dutch | malaysian | brazilian      | american      | turkish |
| City     | boston | marseilles | colone       | miami | liverpool | hamburg | berlin |

