.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, rabbit, pony, cat, chinchilla, rat
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, photography, dancing, magic-tricks, collecting, sudoku, camping
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Pet     | cat | guinea-pig | pony | chinchilla | hamster | rabbit     | rat |
| Hobby   | dancing   | magic-tricks    | camping    | collecting      | photography  | singing | sudoku |

