7 different games are played: domino, canasta, chess, bridge, go, billiard, whist
 1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in may##2
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Birthday   | july  | february   | may         | october     | march              | august    | january     |
