.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, prince, fonseca, bluemaster, dannemann, old-henry
7 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, rabbit, goldfish, rat, dog, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is between the owner of the rat and the oliveros-smoker##2
7. the dannemann-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
8. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Cigar   | old-henry | dannemann       | prince    | bluemaster | fonseca | oliveros     | havana       |
| Pet   | snake    | goldfish | dog | rat        | rabbit | turtle | mouse |

