 3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the bird and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 4. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is the aristoff-smoker##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Pet   | bird | fish | ferret  | guinea-pig   | snake | rabbit | lizard |
| Cigar   | alhambra     | fonseca       | ritmeester | bongani | pall-mall  | tiparillo   | aristoff   |

